This is how you do it.

343
00:35:03,988 --> 00:35:06,757
[airplane whirring]

344
00:35:12,029 --> 00:35:13,630
Are you okay?

345
00:35:15,132 --> 00:35:17,500
Call your mom. Let her know.

346
00:35:50,935 --> 00:35:52,904
Good?

347
00:35:52,937 --> 00:35:54,404
Yeah.

348
00:35:55,072 --> 00:35:57,707
[engine revving]

349
00:36:00,211 --> 00:36:03,480
