It's a long ride.

364
00:37:34,138 --> 00:37:36,240
We're gonna take a few days.

365
00:37:36,273 --> 00:37:37,808
Okay.

366
00:37:42,645 --> 00:37:49,719
♪ I'm staring at water ♪

367
00:37:53,057 --> 00:37:59,063
♪ Trying to... ♪

368
00:38:02,900 --> 00:38:08,671
♪ With my fingertips ♪

369
00:38:12,777 --> 00:38:15,880
[indistinct singing]

370
00:38:22,685 --> 00:38:27,657
♪ Any limit ♪

371
00:38:27,690 --> 00:38:31,694
♪ Every path ♪

372
00:38:34,832 --> 00:38:37,334
♪ Is caught up ♪

373
00:38:37,368 --> 00:38:43,706
♪ In the avalanche ♪

