00:40:08,425 --> 00:40:09,994
Are you alone?

378
00:40:14,198 --> 00:40:15,732
What?

379
00:40:17,801 --> 00:40:19,236
Do you live with anyone?

380
00:40:22,373 --> 00:40:23,941
No.

381
00:40:24,775 --> 00:40:27,744
