394
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:52,156
[music continues]

395
00:43:42,406 --> 00:43:44,007
What?

396
00:43:45,542 --> 00:43:47,177
What did you tell your mom?

397
00:43:50,114 --> 00:43:52,950
