408
00:45:09,259 --> 00:45:10,093
What?

409
00:45:10,127 --> 00:45:11,228
Was I suppose to tell mom,

410
00:45:11,261 --> 00:45:13,230
"Sorry, mom, dad had a total

411
00:45:13,263 --> 00:45:15,165
