413
00:45:16,366 --> 00:45:17,534
That's enough.

414
00:45:19,336 --> 00:45:21,505
I'm the one who shouldn't
be here.

415
00:45:32,516 --> 00:45:34,184
I'm ready, Jack.

416
00:45:37,120 --> 00:45:38,422
[instrumental music]

417
00:45:38,455 --> 00:45:40,491
[engine revving]

418
00:46:05,682 --> 00:46:08,385
[clanging]

419
00:46:26,270 --> 00:46:28,171
