423
00:46:39,851 --> 00:46:41,385
Would you knock it off!

424
00:46:42,319 --> 00:46:43,520
Chill.

425
00:47:03,607 --> 00:47:05,542
[whistling]

426
00:47:08,846 --> 00:47:10,380
[horse snorts]

427
00:47:28,265 --> 00:47:30,701
