00:48:11,274 --> 00:48:15,212
♪ It arrived on my doorstep ♪

433
00:48:15,245 --> 00:48:19,216
♪ A fallen bird from the sky ♪

434
00:48:19,249 --> 00:48:25,656
♪ Lost in the snowstorm
returning home to die ♪

435
00:48:29,292 --> 00:48:34,164
♪ I wrote in cursive to you ♪

