a quick look for ya.

467
00:50:22,006 --> 00:50:24,708
That's very kind, but, you know,
I think we're good.

468
00:50:24,741 --> 00:50:26,610
Aww, don't be silly,
my dad's been working

469
00:50:26,643 --> 00:50:28,745
