470
00:50:30,848 --> 00:50:32,382
I don't want to impose.

471
00:50:32,415 --> 00:50:33,650
Female 2:
Really, not a big deal.

472
00:50:33,683 --> 00:50:35,352
We're just a few
miles outside of town.

473
00:50:36,954 --> 00:50:39,389
Yeah, okay.

