480
00:50:58,441 --> 00:51:00,812
Jack. This is
my daughter, Hanna.

481
00:51:00,845 --> 00:51:01,946
Can I ride with you?

482
00:51:01,979 --> 00:51:04,414
Helen: That okay?
- Yeah.

483
00:51:04,447 --> 00:51:05,615
