484
00:51:05,649 --> 00:51:06,918
- Hanna!
- It's fine.

485
00:51:08,085 --> 00:51:09,619
Of course, you can, sweetie.

486
00:51:11,122 --> 00:51:12,857
Alright, you wanna
follow me, Jack?

487
00:51:14,125 --> 00:51:15,927
Helen: Seat belt on?
Hanna: Yeah.

488
00:51:15,960 --> 00:51:17,094
Helen: Okay.

489
