My dad's an asshole.

506
00:52:23,160 --> 00:52:25,595
Oh, okay.

507
00:52:25,629 --> 00:52:27,631
Yeah, you know what,
I thought he seemed a bit shady.

508
00:52:29,800 --> 00:52:32,402
