935
01:23:04,969 --> 01:23:05,970
No, I'm fine.

936
01:23:06,003 --> 01:23:07,471
Okay, then.

937
01:23:07,504 --> 01:23:08,806
Why don't you eat some
breakfast?

938
01:23:08,840 --> 01:23:10,975
I'll take a quick one,
